text: Wilson is a 1944 American biographical drama movie directed by Henry King and starring Alexander Knox, Charles Coburn, Geraldine Fitzgerald, Thomas Mitchell, Ruth Nelson, Cedric Hardwicke, Vincent Price, Francis X. Bushman. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for 10 Oscars and won 5 Academy Awards in 1945. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1944 drama movies Category:1940s biographical movies Category:American biographical movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Henry King
